reviews.review_text:
Another Smoke Show! Love the Ikos from this time period.  Everything on here is so sweet to hear.

It's crazy-lovely to me that Charlie is still cranking out such stellar mixes after all these years.
Thank you sir, sincerely.

Big thanks to the whole lineage as well, of course.
